{"id": 1950, "genre": 1000, "title": "关于使用信用卡和分期这件事，你有过什么心累的体验？", "description": "移动支付普及的今天，信用消费的概念并没有消失，从银行房贷花呗还款，你在“欠债”这件事上都有什么心酸经历？欢迎在评论区补充！（题图来自：Pixabay)", "record_count": 6191, "comment_count": 25, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201710101548055Reg7823fUXZdrux.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-11T17:00:47Z", "questions": [{"id": 3114, "title": "关于使用信用卡和分期这件事，你有过什么心累的体验？", "content": "关于使用信用卡和分期这件事，你有过什么心累的体验？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 240915, "content": "额度低，基本买不了啥，刷完卡就得还上", "image": "img/option/option/20171011090526WOtRDFVMCAHg6cN3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240917, "content": "提升额度困难，勤刷卡/还款不如常用分期付款等含手续费的服务升得快", "image": "img/option/option/20171010213235oWX6yUrQOAHqjTtE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240918, "content": "还款无限循环，上个iPhone的分期还没还完，又想折旧、分期买新款", "image": "img/option/option/20171010181751s942ABvm0XwCIYNa.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240919, "content": "银行永远在鼓励分期，买双袜子都恨不得让你分期", "image": "img/option/option/20171011152900TCcVpUIYbj5GOx6N.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240920, "content": "不同账单的还款日期容易搞混，处在永远觉得自己要逾期的慌乱中", "image": "img/option/option/20171010155918XviBdVltqN8hG1rE.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240921, "content": "账单太多顾不过来，拆东墙补西墙很焦虑", "image": "img/option/option/20171010181511v6SKTQRYxXkNomPy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240923, "content": "被盗刷，互相推脱不知道找谁说理，申诉花去好多精力", "image": "img/option/option/20171011085937VHPJYyctdph1kg7n.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240925, "content": "外币汇率错乱，海淘/出国旅游常常多交手续费、兑换费", "image": "img/option/option/20171010213536bo5FgMmyBpwGlYR3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240926, "content": "为了返现/返利拼命刷卡，薅羊毛没看清活动细则，白忙活半天", "image": "img/option/option/20171010181144vsIfl9e81YKu7rEO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 240930, "content": "积分体系差劲，好东西兑换门槛高，能换来的都没用", "image": "img/option/option/2017101111335848j90WAbKkxdaORq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}